{"tid":2425652,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭月娥探訪荔枝窩","createTime":"2021-02-27T13:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T13:08:01.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c50f69c03b8fc217416f6fa5d119773569c19609","tid":2425652,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7X8Qqn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7X8Qqn.jpg&h=d7710c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WHwOb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WHwOb3.jpg&h=184c4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWxXJLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWxXJLp.jpg&h=2a513fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【鄉郊辦 x 荔枝窩】<br />\n2018年，環保署之下成立「鄉郊保育辦公室」(鄉郊辦)，以統籌及促進偏遠鄉郊的可持續發展，保育當地的自然生態、建築和人文資源，並促進生態旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，新設「鄉郊保育資助計劃」，支援非牟利團體推展偏遠鄉郊保育及活化工程，支持與村民協作，涵蓋自然保育、活化建築及復育鄉郊文化等項目，由「鄉郊保育諮詢委員會」審視，至今共批17個項目。<br />\n<br />\n今週六清早，落區荔枝窩，聽取鄉郊辦同事匯報工作進展和挑戰，視察「客家生活體驗村」的復育情況，向鄉親父老們問好，並了解偏遠鄉村生活的改善近況。知多啲：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/37QN9dc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37QN9dc&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=aa59471b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/37QN9dc</a><br />\n<br />\n#鄉郊辦：偏遠鄉郊「桃花源」<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3g8xisS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3g8xisS&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d16480f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3g8xisS</a><br />\n<br />\n想知最新環保動向？Follow星星局長IG<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/wongkamsinghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwongkamsinghk&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=ae5ea286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/wongkamsinghk</a> <br />\n<br />\n#復育偏遠鄉郊 #鄉郊保育辦公室 #荔枝窩<br />\n#黃錦星 #wongkamsing"},{"pid":"249c99a2670f147571ad0d539432263e8c2ae37d","tid":2425652,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"連登標準：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2gNmLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2gNmLy.png&h=fbb71260&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcYLSSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcYLSSe.jpg&h=dc9508ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有貢獻<br />\n<br />\n可以懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}